{"tid":1492820,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"望向每雙黑警眼睛 似看到虐待狂身影","createTime":"2019-08-21T04:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T04:52:43.000Z","uid":114110,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"63a8b274cc855f4b1b9b4a2c876ab2a14a299565","tid":1492820,"uid":114110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:03:59.000Z","msg":"近排咁多負面新聞 咁大壓力<br />\n搞到小弟成日聽嚮往自由既歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n望向每雙黑警眼睛<br />\n似看到虐待狂身影<br />\n被虐那刻失聲痛哭<br />\n哪裡有綻放的紫荊<br />\n<br />\n在這暗房中間紮綁<br />\n有布壓有極權饕饕<br />\n在這一刻想起往悉<br />\n哪裡有橄欖枝花季<br />\n<br />\nOhohohohohyayayay呀呀呀呀<br />\n<br />\n良知的缺失竟得到寛待<br />\n而冷理百萬市民想法<br />\n如殘暴仍然能被改寫<br />\n畜牲的改寫聖者<br />\n我真係屌你老母～<br />\n<br />\n願這抗戰成神話<br />\n賭上生命實現它<br />\n未來幸福的希冀<br />\n為自由每夜去奔波<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇大神完成埋下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22fe30e120eb5048b2838130cef4f948f438064","tid":1492820,"uid":114110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:07:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97f5d443cd1a8c9f792121917a91d7b93030df08","tid":1492820,"uid":114110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:08:12.000Z","msg":"冇大神完成埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"be4758da38047b8dab3c197e26a9fe2f6cf8d511","tid":1492820,"uid":38253,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:11:09.00